snippet.title: A Sandbox Game to Play with Friends!
snippet.description:
Create your very own avatar, call all your friends, and get ready to discover PK XD!

An open world to explore every corner and have the best of fun. 😎

Download now and start playing:
https://pkxd.onelink.me/V7Ue
